{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":57,"text":"The story I want to tell you about, started to me,"},{"time":3673,"text":"in 1996 when I was studying in England."},{"time":7825,"text":"One day, I was glancing through my bank statement\n(I didn't have much to look at)"},{"time":11989,"text":"and I've noticed that in the upper corner there was\na symbol, that I'm going to show you,"},{"time":17331,"text":"saying that document had been made in\nplain language, for me to understand it."},{"time":21790,"text":"The idea interested me; I tried to find out\nwhat that was"},{"time":24130,"text":"and I found out that there was a campaign for the\nsimplification of language,"},{"time":28298,"text":"which was the \"Plain English Campaign\"."},{"time":30085,"text":"I thought it was a fabulous idea, for about \none day or two,"},{"time":33010,"text":"and I've never thought about it since."},{"time":34810,"text":"When I came back to Portugal, for good,"},{"time":37285,"text":"I came across with several documents - for example, \nmy work contract,"},{"time":42430,"text":"the papers I had to sign to buy a house, \nthe electricity bill --"},{"time":47127,"text":"a series of documents that reminded me of \nthat bank statement."},{"time":50528,"text":"Not because they were equally clear and simple,"},{"time":54105,"text":"but because they were the exact opposite."},{"time":56711,"text":"Because I had to read everything twice or thrice, \nto begin to understand what was written there."},{"time":61505,"text":"And then, that little seed that had been sown\nin 1996, started germinating."},{"time":68423,"text":"And one day, I found myself"},{"time":70174,"text":"entering through my boss' office and quitting \nmy job to dedicate myself to this."},{"time":74174,"text":"And so, what did I find out, right off the start?"},{"time":77634,"text":"I found out that it was a much more severe problem \nthan I thought."},{"time":80558,"text":"It wasn't only about these documents being \ncomplex and annoying,"},{"time":85024,"text":"it was the fact that Portuguese people's literacy --"},{"time":88324,"text":"literacy is the hability to understand written documents --"},{"time":91159,"text":"is extremely low. I'm going to show you a chart about Portuguese people's literacy [rate]."},{"time":96692,"text":"You know that about 10, 11% of people, in Portugal,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":100273,"text":"don't know how to read nor write at all, yet."},{"time":103082,"text":"Over there are those who know, or say they know, \nhow to read and write. So, what do we have?"},{"time":107297,"text":"We have that group of red people in level 1, \nwhich is the lowest in literacy [rate]."},{"time":112657,"text":"They are persons who are able to join letters,"},{"time":115981,"text":"but they can't, actually, understand."},{"time":118529,"text":"For example, if a person, from that red group, \nhas to pick up"},{"time":122216,"text":"the package leaflet of a medicinal product, \nto give a dose of medicine to his/her child,"},{"time":127496,"text":"he/she can't, can't understand the information."},{"time":129965,"text":"50% of the Portuguese. Then we have 30% more, \nthose yellow ones,"},{"time":135093,"text":"over there, people who get by\non the daily basis."},{"time":139644,"text":"That is, if they don't have to read anything too new \nor too different, they will manage."},{"time":143018,"text":"But, for example, if they work in a factory and \na new machine arrives"},{"time":146718,"text":"and they have to read the machine's manual \nto be able to work with it, they can't do it anymore."},{"time":151616,"text":"And there they go, 80% of the Portuguese people."},{"time":156068,"text":"Then we have a few more that can handle documents,"},{"time":158684,"text":"as long as they are not too complex,"},{"time":160111,"text":"and we have 5% of the population that \ncan handle really complex documents."},{"time":165550,"text":"Now, just so you don't think this is normal, \nthat over there is Sweden."},{"time":170587,"text":"While we have 20% of people with the literacy \nconsidered essential for a daily basis,"},{"time":175936,"text":"Sweden has 75%."},{"time":179453,"text":"And looking at that, what did I realize?"},{"time":181561,"text":"I realized we live in an apartheid of information."},{"time":184896,"text":"I realized that there's a small minority of people \nwho has indeed access to information"},{"time":190647,"text":"and can use it to their advantage and \na huge majority that can't."},{"time":196041,"text":"And because they can't, they are excluded \nand they are impaired."},{"time":199847,"text":"Let me give you an example."},{"time":201863,"text":"That one is Mr. Domingos, my building's doorkeeper. Mr. Domingos started to read at the age of 27,"},{"time":207230,"text":"so, he falls in that yellow group that \nwe have seen a little while ago."},{"time":210278,"text":"From time to time, I'm arriving home and he says:"},{"time":212231,"text":"\"Miss Sandra!\"; \"Yes, Mr. Domingos.\""},{"time":214362,"text":"\"Here is a little letter.\" So, the deal is: when Mr. Domingos or someone in the family or in the neighbourhood"},{"time":218881,"text":"receives something that they don't understand, \nthey come to me and I help them to translate it."},{"time":222576,"text":"And so, that time he said to me like this:"},{"time":224186,"text":"\"Oh, Miss Sandra, I'm about to throw this away, \nbut check it if this is important.\""},{"time":227911,"text":"It was very important. He had been waiting, \nfor quite a while, to have a knee surgery"},{"time":232737,"text":"and that was the letter of the famous surgery-bank\nchecks. When a person is waiting for a long time,"},{"time":236597,"text":"they get a bank check and with that bank check \nthey can have that surgery in the private sector."},{"time":240288,"text":"It was almost thrown away into the garbage, \nMr. Domingos' letter."},{"time":243324,"text":"In that same year, I've found out,"},{"time":245475,"text":"only 20% of people had used these \nsurgery-bank checks."},{"time":249069,"text":"The other 80%, I don't believe they had been cured\nwhile they were waiting."},{"time":255156,"text":"They most likely did the same as Mr. Domingos:"},{"time":258192,"text":"\"Ah! What's this? I'm not understanding, \nit's going to the garbage\"."},{"time":260487,"text":"They lost the opportunity to have the surgery \nthey needed."},{"time":263436,"text":"What happens here? When people don't understand"},{"time":267739,"text":"this has severe consequences -- to the individual, \nbut also for the country."},{"time":271307,"text":"When I don't understand which are my rights, \nthe benefits I can have access to,"},{"time":274519,"text":"I can't understand my duties and I'm not \nan active and participative citizen either."},{"time":279368,"text":"Now, maybe, you are sitting there and thinking:"},{"time":283428,"text":"\"Yeah, poor Mr. Domingos... Bad luck, isn't it? \nMe?! I'm in the green ones.\""},{"time":287415,"text":"\"I'm absolutely sure that I'm one of the green ones. \nI was selected to come to TED! Hum?\" (Laughter)"},{"time":291468,"text":"So the deal is: I have here some texts to read to you"},{"time":295796,"text":"and I'm going to see what color are you \nwhen I finish reading."},{"time":299640,"text":"So, come on, this is an automobile insurance \ncontract. It says this:"},{"time":303339,"text":"\"Unless contrary stipulation, the decease of the ensured person, the ensured capital is provided,"},{"time":309825,"text":"in case of predeceasing of the beneficiary relatively to the ensured person, to the heirs of the last,"},{"time":315660,"text":"in case of the simultaneous decease of the ensured person and of the beneficiary,"},{"time":319089,"text":"to the heirs of the last\". Hum? (Laughter)"},{"time":321491,"text":"Next, there's another one, from the medicines' \npackage leaflet, that says the following:"},{"time":326535,"text":"\"Warning! It may also occur erythema, edema, \nvesiculation, keratolysis and urticaria.\""},{"time":333999,"text":"Hum? Are you clear?"},{"time":337005,"text":"And this one is really good. This one, I signed\na renting contract to the new office on Friday"},{"time":340396,"text":"and I laughed my head off."},{"time":341724,"text":"So, it said: \"I, as a cosigner, assume the opportune \npayment of the rents,"},{"time":347284,"text":"waiving the benefits of the division \nand prior foreclosure.\""},{"time":351100,"text":"When I heard \"opportune payment\" [\"storm payment\" \nin Portuguese], I imagined myself bursting in there,"},{"time":354612,"text":"slamming the door and saying: \"Here's the money!!!\"\n(Laughter)"},{"time":358498,"text":"But it's not! (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":359847,"text":"But it's not! (Applause)"},{"time":360796,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":362001,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":364999,"text":"So, it's this: when we leave our area of expertise --"},{"time":368983,"text":"and it only takes a little; there is no need to go \nto the string theory or something like that,"},{"time":372612,"text":"it only takes a little... (Laughter)"},{"time":374202,"text":"What happens?"},{"time":375943,"text":"We get as lost as Mr. Domingos."},{"time":379639,"text":"And these documents are not written \nby experts to experts,"},{"time":383612,"text":"as the ones from the string theory."},{"time":385461,"text":"No! These are documents written for me, \nthese are the public documents,"},{"time":388909,"text":"the public documents I need to understand \nin my daily life,"},{"time":392613,"text":"to govern myself, to live my life."},{"time":394203,"text":"These are the renting contracts, the package leaflet \nof the medicines."},{"time":396938,"text":"It's all this. The electricity bills."},{"time":400096,"text":"This has to be clear, so that I can understand."},{"time":401969,"text":"Because, if I can't understand, what happens?"},{"time":404329,"text":"I make mistakes, I get wrong."},{"time":407658,"text":"I'm going to give you an example of mistakes that \nwere committed, bad decisions made"},{"time":411691,"text":"for not being able to understand documents."},{"time":413935,"text":"Do you remember the subprime crisis that \ntook place in the United States?"},{"time":417674,"text":"What happened?"},{"time":419871,"text":"People signed those loans to buy houses,"},{"time":422848,"text":"without truly understanding what they were signing."},{"time":425071,"text":"Because if they knew what they were signing,"},{"time":427335,"text":"they'd know that as soon as the interest rate started\nto rise, the monthly payment would also increase,"},{"time":433485,"text":"they wouldn't be able to pay anymore and \nthey would end up without a house."},{"time":436669,"text":"So, the rest, after that, next, everything \ncrumbled down and we know the rest."},{"time":440726,"text":"Do you think that if there was a culture of clarity \nin the financial sector"},{"time":445989,"text":"things would have got up to where they've got?"},{"time":448016,"text":"I don't think so. So,"},{"time":451521,"text":"how do you solve this problem,"},{"time":454909,"text":"this such big difference between the \nliteracy [rate] of the Portuguese,"},{"time":458097,"text":"that is down here, and the complexity \nof the public documents,"},{"time":461116,"text":"those ones we need to understand\nin our daily lives, sorry,"},{"time":464583,"text":"that are up here?"},{"time":466157,"text":"So, the first think that comes to mind is,"},{"time":468728,"text":"\"If literacy is down here, let's make it rise\" -- isn't it?"},{"time":472004,"text":"Let's educate people."},{"time":473942,"text":"Let's, let's... of course we will, \nof course we will educate people."},{"time":477077,"text":"The thing is, it's hard and it's slow. \nAnd I don't even want to imagine"},{"time":481196,"text":"how many generations it will take until we are \nat Sweden's level."},{"time":485351,"text":"But, besides that, it's not only because it is slow. \nThere is another problem."},{"time":487848,"text":"If the language of the documents \nisn't simpler,"},{"time":491681,"text":"we've already seen that people, even with \na high literacy level, like you,"},{"time":496680,"text":"if the language is hard, they don't get cleared,"},{"time":499844,"text":"they continue to be unable to understand\nthese documents."},{"time":502742,"text":"So, besides increasing literacy [rate], and for now,"},{"time":506746,"text":"it's much more important to reduce \nthe complexity of documents"},{"time":510901,"text":"and simplify the language."},{"time":515304,"text":"I'm going to show you an example."},{"time":517305,"text":"When I talk about simplifying the language. \nNotice!"},{"time":519306,"text":"On the left side of a contract:"},{"time":523381,"text":"\"It is agreed that the insurance company, bla bla bla, \nbla bla bla, bla bla...\""},{"time":526815,"text":"This is a before and after example. What do we mean with simplifying language?"},{"time":531314,"text":"It's communicating in a simple and clear way, \nenabling our reader to understand it at first glance."},{"time":539119,"text":"What do you prefer? Before or after?"},{"time":543043,"text":"There isn't much doubt, is there?"},{"time":545311,"text":"So, how is this achieved? How can you make \nthe State and companies communicate"},{"time":551449,"text":"with citizens in a language they can understand \nat first glance?"},{"time":554658,"text":"There are several ways. There are countries \nthat are going by the path of legislation."},{"time":558079,"text":"For example, Sweden and the United States \nintroduced, last year, a legislation that forces"},{"time":564144,"text":"the State to communicate with people in \na language they can understand."},{"time":567649,"text":"And you think, \"Well, that's normal. \nThey are countries that are a bit ahead."},{"time":570654,"text":"\"Sweden, maybe, much more than the United States."},{"time":573115,"text":"\"But they are countries that are a bit ahead."},{"time":574765,"text":"\"It would be nice if in our country there was also \nlegislation towards that, wouldn't it be?\""},{"time":578314,"text":"So it would. And there is! Since 1999."},{"time":582862,"text":"The Law of the Administrative Modernization \nsays that"},{"time":585584,"text":"the communication between the State and the people"},{"time":588260,"text":"should be simple, clear, concise, meaningful, \nwithout acronyms, bla bla bla..."},{"time":593613,"text":"But the thing is: it is not applied. So, the question,"},{"time":595660,"text":"the path of going through legislation, \nenforcing through legislation,"},{"time":598928,"text":"works in those countries where laws \nare made to be applied."},{"time":602922,"text":"Now, there is another way, the way of marketing."},{"time":607493,"text":"How does that work? It's like this:"},{"time":610200,"text":"private companies change their language; \ncommunicate in a clearer and simpler way,"},{"time":614847,"text":"they make a big fuss about it, consumers love it,"},{"time":617109,"text":"the sales rise, it works beautifully."},{"time":619983,"text":"But it works for the private sector."},{"time":621973,"text":"Now, what is the third path, and to me, \nthe most important one?"},{"time":627020,"text":"It's the path of civil movements,"},{"time":629316,"text":"that are based in a mentality shift."},{"time":631987,"text":"In countries where this really went forward --"},{"time":634628,"text":"do you remember the English label, of the\n\"Plain English Campaign\"? --"},{"time":636787,"text":"this is all based on a consumers' movement."},{"time":639976,"text":"So, what does it take for that civic movement \nto happen?"},{"time":644503,"text":"We need to understand two very important things:"},{"time":647350,"text":"First, wanting to understand these \npublic documents is not a whim,"},{"time":652381,"text":"is not an intellectual curiosity."},{"time":654729,"text":"It is a necessity that I have in my daily life."},{"time":656897,"text":"And above all, it is a right, it is everyone's right."},{"time":660045,"text":"On this side we have: understanding is a right."},{"time":663790,"text":"And we have to understand another thing too,"},{"time":665410,"text":"which is: he who writes, has to write in order \nto be understood."},{"time":668983,"text":"How do we get there?"},{"time":671034,"text":"First of all: we have to become demanding \nconsumers and citizens."},{"time":675960,"text":"Think it this way: next time someone \ngives you a document"},{"time":680435,"text":"that you just simply don't understand, don't be shy,"},{"time":683428,"text":"don't keep quiet, pretending that you are \nunderstanding everything."},{"time":686152,"text":"No! Demand to understand. Ask."},{"time":688772,"text":"I know that this is not easy. Turn to the gentleman \nin the little suite and say:"},{"time":692067,"text":"\"Look here, this contract, this part, \nwhat does this mean?\""},{"time":695197,"text":"It's not easy, and perhaps it's even a bit \nembarrassing, isn't it?"},{"time":699411,"text":"But it is not. It's a sign of intelligence."},{"time":701444,"text":"What do you teach your children when \nthey have doubts in school?"},{"time":704984,"text":"\"Don't say nothing to anyone, shut up really good \nand act smart.\""},{"time":708573,"text":"No, you don't, right? You say:"},{"time":710357,"text":"\"Look, when you don't understand, you put your hand \nup in the air and ask the teacher until you are cleared.\""},{"time":714216,"text":"And that is exactly what we have to do, \nas consumers and citizens."},{"time":718220,"text":"So, next time you come across with \na document you don't understand,"},{"time":722845,"text":"demand to understand, put aside your pride and ask"},{"time":725651,"text":"until you get completely cleared."},{"time":727791,"text":"Then, there's the other side, which is:\n\"Okay, these awful documents"},{"time":733282,"text":"\"which are in circulation, they don't grow on trees."},{"time":735389,"text":"\"Someone wrote them.\" Hum?"},{"time":737483,"text":"Maybe, among this big group, some persons..."},{"time":741986,"text":"I don't know, some lawyers, some public employees --\nI'm not asking you to identify yourselves,"},{"time":746639,"text":"but I ask you to search your own conscience."},{"time":749172,"text":"How many times do you write documents \nfor the general public,"},{"time":752511,"text":"for people that don't share your language,"},{"time":755127,"text":"and you write them in a language that \nonly you will understand?"},{"time":757796,"text":"And you'll say: \"Ah, that's because \nthere is a reason, here!\""},{"time":760821,"text":"Dear friends, I already heard all the reasons."},{"time":762413,"text":"There are thousands of reasons. They go like these:"},{"time":765178,"text":"\"Ah, it's the house's culture\"; \"Oh, my boss!\""},{"time":767152,"text":"\"Oh, the judge! And what if this goes to court?\""},{"time":769927,"text":"\"What you want is to destroy language. \nWe have to educate people.\""},{"time":772508,"text":"\"We can't lower the level\"; bla, bla, bla..."},{"time":774483,"text":"I've seen all of this. These are excuses."},{"time":776904,"text":"A while ago, they told us about Einstein."},{"time":779475,"text":"Einstein said this: \"If you can't write about a subject,"},{"time":783353,"text":"in a simple way, it's because, in fact, \nyou don't understand it.\""},{"time":786093,"text":"So, if you... (Applause)"},{"time":789637,"text":"To Einstein... (Applause)"},{"time":791547,"text":"To Einstein...(Applause)"},{"time":793208,"text":"So -- ah, ah, I don't have time! --"},{"time":795907,"text":"so, if you do know what you want to say -- \ndon't you? --"},{"time":800479,"text":"you are aware of what you want to say,"},{"time":802645,"text":"you just have to do one thing: believe that it is \npossible to write in a simple way."},{"time":807385,"text":"And how do you do that?"},{"time":809123,"text":"It's very easy. You write to your grandmother. \nHum?"},{"time":813034,"text":"You write to your grandmother. I'm going \nto show grandma to you."},{"time":814882,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":817192,"text":"You write with respect and without paternalism."},{"time":818951,"text":"And you use three techniques that I'm going \nto teach you. First of all:"},{"time":822450,"text":"Start by the most important."},{"time":824686,"text":"Grandma has a lot to do. She is not going to read\nthree pages to get to the main idea."},{"time":828565,"text":"Start by the most important."},{"time":830766,"text":"Next, use short sentences, because grandma,"},{"time":834438,"text":"like anyone of us,"},{"time":835648,"text":"if you make very long sentences,"},{"time":837325,"text":"she gets to the end and she can't remember what \nyou said in the beginning, anymore."},{"time":839859,"text":"And lastly, the third, use plain words, those ones \nthat grandma knows."},{"time":844515,"text":"Alright? It's easy!"},{"time":846833,"text":"Before I leave,"},{"time":848398,"text":"I would like to talk to you about \"Clara\" (Clear). \n\"Clara\" is a project of social responsibility."},{"time":851416,"text":"It has this mission: to change the way how public communication is made."},{"time":855308,"text":"What do we do?"},{"time":856239,"text":"We are going to launch this year \na collection of \"Claro\" guides,"},{"time":860026,"text":"that is, we are going to pick very, very, \nvery complex subjects and put them simple."},{"time":864123,"text":"We are going to start with the \n\"Claro\" Guide of Justice."},{"time":866303,"text":"I think it is an area... that comes in handy. \n(Applause)"},{"time":870170,"text":"And now I'm going to follow Manuel [Forjaz]'s advise. \nIf it's time to ask,"},{"time":872752,"text":"whoever wants to sponsor the \n\"Claro\" Guide of Justice -- I don't know..."},{"time":875766,"text":"for example, the EDP Foundation, or...ha? --"},{"time":878834,"text":"come talk to me later."},{"time":881712,"text":"Another thing we will do is to grant prizes \nto the worse and best documents,"},{"time":886046,"text":"because, indeed, there are people who are working\nto communicate in a clearer way,"},{"time":889565,"text":"and that have to be rewarded,"},{"time":890814,"text":"and there are lazy people that do nothing \nabout it and need to be humiliated."},{"time":894407,"text":"So, we'll give prizes to the worst and to the best."},{"time":896812,"text":"I'm counting on your help. (Applause)"},{"time":898553,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":903076,"text":"We are going to launch... we are going to launch\nthe campaign via Clara's Facebook,"},{"time":907091,"text":"so, send your friendship request and \nyou'll be up to date."},{"time":910182,"text":"But, lastly, above all, what does \"Clara\" want?"},{"time":912608,"text":"It wants to put two little things in your heads."},{"time":914425,"text":"The first one: demand to understand. Don't be shy."},{"time":918069,"text":"And write in order to be understood. \nWrite to your grandma."},{"time":922350,"text":"And if you don't have a grandmother, write to \nMr. Domingos, he will like it."},{"time":926766,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}